# G&W port: keep only what the Game & Watch HAL compiles
# (NRF52840Doom/Doom/{source,include}) + the WAD converter source + reference
# HAL/licence. Exclude the nRF-specific SDK copies, build output and the
# separate wireless-keyboard firmware (none are compiled by this repo).
